"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750943","Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","false","2017-07-18","<p>The Government is in the process of devolving the onshore licensing regime to give the Scottish Government more control over the development of these resources. The Scottish Government already has responsibility for the planning and environmental aspects of the onshore oil and gas regime.</p>","Watford","Richard Harrington",,"2017-07-18T15:11:02.833Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750943/answer","Biography information for Richard Harrington","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750943/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750943/answer","Watford","Richard Harrington","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750943/answer/previousversion/5109","Biography information for Richard Harrington","201","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","2017-07-11","Fracking: Scotland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, what plans he has to support the shale industry in Scotland; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Deidre Brock","Edinburgh North and Leith","Deidre  Brock","4317"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750944","Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","false","2017-07-20","<p>The Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy does not hold the information you have asked for. Ministers regularly undertake engagements at which media are present.</p>","Stourbridge","Margot James",,"2017-07-20T16:34:21.483Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750944/answer","Biography information for Margot James","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750944/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750944/answer",,,,,"201","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","2017-07-11","Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy: Mass Media","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, how many public engagements for which a media calling notice was issued was attended by a departmental Minister in each of the last 12 months.","false","Biography information for Deidre Brock","Edinburgh North and Leith","Deidre  Brock","4295"
