"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749997","Home Office","false","2018-02-19","<p>It is Government policy not to publish directions by the PM to the Intelligence Services Commissioner.</p>","Wyre and Preston North","Mr Ben Wallace",,"2018-02-19T16:31:04.887Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749997/answer","Biography information for Mr Ben Wallace","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749997/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749997/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2017-07-10","Intelligence Services Commissioner","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, if she will publish the third direction issued by the Prime Minister to the Intelligence Services Commissioner.","false","Biography information for Emily Thornberry","Islington South and Finsbury","Emily Thornberry","4052"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749998","Cabinet Office","false","2017-07-19","<p>Cabinet Office does not hold a central record of contracts being terminated or restarted during this period.</p>","Romsey and Southampton North","Caroline Nokes",,"2017-07-19T15:31:58.887Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749998/answer","Biography information for Caroline Nokes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749998/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/749998/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2017-07-10","Cabinet Office: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many contracts put out to tender by his Department have been (a) cancelled and (b) re-tendered in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","3998"
