"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750145","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2017-07-17","<p>The Foreign Secretary discussed the situation in Yemen with the Crown Prince of Saudi Arabia on 7 July. I also spoke to the Saudi Ambassador on 10 July.</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt",,"2017-07-17T14:24:53.073Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750145/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750145/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750145/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2017-07-10","Yemen: Military Intervention","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, what recent representations he has made to the Government of Saudi Arabia on the situation in Yemen.","false","Biography information for Keith Vaz","Leicester East","Keith Vaz","4066"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750146","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2017-07-18","<p>The Foreign Secretary met Sheikh Mohammed bin Abdulrahman al-Thani, the Qatari Foreign Minister, in London on 26 June to relay UK concerns about tensions between Qatar and its neighbours and to reassure him of the UK's willingness to help resolve the situation. The UK continues to call for de-escalation and are firmly behind Kuwait's mediation efforts.</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt",,"2017-07-18T15:56:41.297Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750146/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750146/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750146/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2017-07-10","Qatar: Foreign Relations","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, when he last met his Qatari counterpart; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Keith Vaz","Leicester East","Keith Vaz","4067"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750147","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2017-07-17","<p>​The UK continues to support the work of the current UN Special Envoy and his tireless efforts in working with all parties to bring about peace in Yemen.</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt",,"2017-07-17T14:38:17.287Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750147/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750147/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750147/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2017-07-10","Yemen: Foreign Relations","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, when he plans to appoint a new Special Envoy for Yemen.","false","Biography information for Keith Vaz","Leicester East","Keith Vaz","4068"
